      "content": "everything just feels like too much. i've spent 5 years on this research and it's all falling apart. the funding is gone, the lab is basically shutting down, and i feel like there's literally nothing left of me outside of this work. i'm just so tired of fighting to keep things from collapsing. i just want the noise to stop.",
